<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="484" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1435,831,1037]" box="[199,1179,868,893]" pageId="9" pageNumber="484">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,1017,868,893]" pageId="9" pageNumber="484">Recorded damage and economic importance in the orchards of Iran:</emphasis>
Not recorded.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1435,831,1037]" pageId="9" pageNumber="484">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,938,903,928]" pageId="9" pageNumber="484">Recorded damage in the orchards of other parts of the world:</emphasis>
A potential vector for the bacterium 
<taxonomicName class="Gammaproteobacteria" family="Xanthomonadaceae" genus="Xylella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Bacteria" order="Xanthomonadales" pageId="9" pageNumber="484" phylum="Proteobacteria" rank="species" species="fastidiosa">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="484">Xylella fastidiosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
which infests olive trees in New Zealand (Anonymous 2013).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1435,831,1037]" box="[199,1107,975,1000]" pageId="9" pageNumber="484">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,562,975,1000]" pageId="9" pageNumber="484">Recorded distribution in Iran:</emphasis>
North and centre (
<bibRefCitation box="[771,1095,975,1000]" pageId="9" pageNumber="484" refId="ref20791" refString="Mozaffarian, F. &amp; Wilson, M. R. (2015) The aphrophorid spittlebugs of Iran (Hemiptera: Cercopoidea: Aphrophoridae). Zootaxa, 4052 (4), 442 - 456. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4052.4.2" type="journal article">Mozaffarian &amp; Wilson 2015</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1435,831,1037]" box="[199,1311,1012,1037]" pageId="9" pageNumber="484">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,342,1012,1037]" pageId="9" pageNumber="484">Conclusion:</emphasis>
The role of the species in transmitting 
<taxonomicName box="[780,976,1012,1037]" class="Gammaproteobacteria" family="Xanthomonadaceae" genus="Xylella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Bacteria" order="Xanthomonadales" pageId="9" pageNumber="484" phylum="Proteobacteria" rank="species" species="fastidiosa">
<emphasis box="[780,976,1012,1037]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="484">Xylella fastidiosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
needs to be evaluated in Iran.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
